## 1. mbuzz — Best for Model Flexibility

**Why consider mbuzz:** Dreamdata shows attribution. mbuzz lets you compare 8 models side-by-side and build custom logic.

### What mbuzz Offers

**Server-side tracking that Dreamdata can't match.** Dreamdata relies on client-side JavaScript that ad blockers defeat. mbuzz tracks on your backend—capture 95%+ of touchpoints across the entire B2B buying journey.

**8 attribution models with side-by-side comparison.** See how the same deal gets credited under First Touch, Last Touch, Linear, Time Decay, U-Shaped, W-Shaped, Markov Chain, and Shapley Value. Dreamdata shows journeys; mbuzz shows how different models interpret those journeys.

<figure class="my-8">
  <%= image_tag "/images/product/attribution/model-comparison.png", alt: "mbuzz model comparison showing Linear vs Markov Chain attribution side-by-side", class: "rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm w-full" %>
  <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">Compare how different models interpret the same B2B journey</figcaption>
</figure>

**Custom attribution rules in minutes.** Don't wait for feature requests—define your own logic:

```ruby
# Credit content downloads heavily, weight branded search lower
model "content_led_growth" do
  if event_type == "content_download" && content_gated?
    weight 0.35
  elsif channel == "paid_search" && query.branded?
    weight 0.10
  else
    weight :time_decay
  end
end
```

**LTV attribution for SaaS.** Track expansion, renewals, and churn back to original acquisition source. That enterprise campaign might have high CAC but 140% NDR—mbuzz shows the full picture.

**Transparent, affordable pricing:**

| Tier | Records/Month | Price |
|------|-------------|-------|
| Free | Up to <%= free_event_limit_display %> | $0 |
| Starter | Up to 1M | $29/mo |
| Growth | Up to 5M | $99/mo |
| Pro | Up to 25M | $299/mo |

**10-minute setup** with native SDKs for Rails, Django, Laravel, and Node.js. No 4-8 week implementation projects.

### mbuzz vs Dreamdata

| Factor | Dreamdata | mbuzz |
|--------|-----------|-------|
| Journey visualization | ★★★★★ | ★★★★☆ |
| Custom models | Limited | ✓ 8 + DSL |
| Enterprise ABM | Limited | Check |
| Setup time | 4-8 weeks | Varies |
| Free tier | ✓ Yes | Check |

### Why mbuzz Over Dreamdata

Dreamdata excels at showing customer journeys. But how do you know the attribution credit is accurate? mbuzz validates with custom attribution models.

### Best For

- Teams wanting proof, not just visualization
- Enterprise B2B with complex needs
- Those skeptical of unvalidated MTA
- Companies with budget for accuracy

